divs: Sighting DetailsPulled into gas station, girlfriend went into store. Looked into sky and saw two glowing white objects heading toward Lake Huron. Got out of truck and grapped my digital camera. Snapped a couple pics with the flash on. Turned on the video mode and shot two clips. The objects were brighter than Venus,wich was nearby. Both objects were going same direction and about same alt. Watched for about two minutes before objects faded out.
Summary: Observed two UFO'S at gas station
